a. Create new Dynamic web project
  MySoapService

b. add a package in Java Resources
c. create a simple class

public class HelloWorld 
{

    public String sayHelloWorld(String name)
    {
        return "Hello world from "+ name;
    }
}  

d. Select project - new - web service

e. select service type - Bottom up java code
   service implementation as the the package and class name

f. New project is created

g. start server  
